Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:68512,71849}{\i1}The city of fog, London.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71849,76395}{\i1}After overcoming numerous dangers,\NIsabelle and Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76395,80482}{\i1}finally arrived\Nat their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:80941,83986}Excuse me, do you know someone\Nnamed Martin Schmidt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83986,85863}Is Mr. Martin Schmidt here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:86196,88949}Martin?\NCan't say it rings a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93078,95623}– What are you doing?\N– "What are you doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95623,99835}Ha. If you don't like the smoke of a cigar,\Nyou'd better get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99835,103505}This is not the place for such munchkins,\Nall wet behind their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103505,104548}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104548,106508}Oh, did I upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106508,111388}If you're such a man, why don't you take your\Npants off and show what you have under?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111388,113390}Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116393,118437}Come on! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118437,120230}We're all waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122024,123609}Give them a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125152,127780}One of you is Isabelle\Nand you have news from Paris, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127780,129740}Paris? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130574,132451}How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132910,137081}I've heard a bit about Jules from Paris.\NI will introduce you to Martin Schmidt.
